<p>此异常脚踝处的文字在当天变为：</p>
<div class="wiki-note">
<p>SCP-096, the shy guy<br />
happy April Fools' Day!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;新增：2020/7/03</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;隐藏</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>因在2020/7/01，此异常变为无法摧毁的雕像后失去了所有异常性质，对于将此异常列为正式的SCP的申请已被驳回。</p>
