<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00483/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个██牌的酸奶瓶，当任意人类的舌头触碰瓶盖内部时，瓶盖内部会以█ml/s的速率产出原成分酸奶。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>陈博士的书桌<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>由site-█食堂自助餐区保管<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><br />
我说不会真的有人想舔我用过的瓶盖吧？<br />
——陈博士<br />
我们会对使用过的瓶盖定期清理消毒，请放心<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">使</span>食用。<br />
——site —█的食堂主管</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00483" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00483" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00483-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blue-melody" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6733419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6733419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200735" alt="blue_melody" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6733419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blue-melody" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6733419); return false;">blue_melody</a></span></p>
